{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 116069, "create_time": 1652582363, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "中美相比的话，美国应该算小政府，政府不会当爹，中国政府才是爹", "timestamp": 1652582363}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 116070, "create_time": 1652582380, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "政府应该管你的一切，你被诈骗政府也要管，就是什么都被政府强制管一管才比较好。政府卖力气宣传还不够，没有政府管，你的钱就会被电信诈骗的骗走。", "timestamp": 1652582380}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 116080, "create_time": 1652582628, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "就好像你有一个慈爱的父亲，这不让那也不让，并念念有词地说是“为你好”。你心甘情愿地接受，还为自己的权利不同程度地被剥夺而叫好", "timestamp": 1652582628}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 116083, "create_time": 1652582704, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "这也是没有办法的事情，中国老百姓早就习惯了政府什么都管，如果自己被骗了，会去找政府、要求政府来负责的。这个情况下政府只能管得越来越多。", "timestamp": 1652582704}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 116087, "create_time": 1652582775, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re : 我要吃饭自由，我要喝水自由，我才不管其他人会不会被噎死或者呛死捏😁", "timestamp": 1652582775}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 116089, "create_time": 1652582812, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "我认为，中国现行政治制度确实是适合中国国情的。不喜欢这种爹味政府的话，要么忍着，要么让自己去适应它，要么用脚投票", "timestamp": 1652582812}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 116097, "create_time": 1652582922, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "吃饭太可怕了，吃饭居然有可能会噎死人，我们要全面禁止吃饭。", "timestamp": 1652582922}, {"autho